**PyFotMob** is a python module to streamline your interaction with the FotMob API. Access real-time football information for your applications. From analysis tools to news feeds and betting algorithms, PyFotMob offers a seamless interface for fixture details, live scores, player stats, and team info. Elevate your Python projects with accurate football data using PyFotMob ‚öΩ.

